#: convertibleYes
msgid "Your message can be converted to plain text without losing information."
msgstr "Mae modd trosi eich neges i destun plaen heb golli unrhyw wybodaeth."

#: convertibleAltering
msgid ""
"Your message can be converted to plain text without losing important "
"information. However, the plain text version might look different from what "
"you saw in the composer."
msgstr ""
"Mae modd trosi eich neges i destun plaen heb golli gwybodaeth bwysig. Fodd "
"bynnag, gall y fersiwn testun plaen edrych yn wahanol i'r hyn oedd yn y "
"cyfansoddwr."

#: convertibleNo
msgid ""
"However, you used formatting (e.g. colors) that will not be converted to "
"plain text."
msgstr ""
"Er hynny, rydych wedi defnyddio fformatio (e.e lliwiau) na fydd yn cael ei "
"drosi i destun plaen."

